<body>
<h2>What's New in 1.7</h2>  <ul><li><strong>Dual-ring menu bar</strong> — the icon now shows two concentric arcs: outer for your 5h window, inner for the 7-day. The inner ring stays dim when you're safe, brightens to amber/red as you approach the weekly cliff — the limit that actually cuts you off for days.</li>  <li><strong>Freshness cue</strong> — a subtle "just now / 2m ago" timestamp in the popover footer so you always know how stale the data is.</li>  <li><strong>Widget polish</strong> — gauges are larger, padding tighter, and the refresh button now sits cleanly inline below the reset time instead of floating off the edge.</li></ul>
</body>
